        <Meaning id="6f5e104d-e790-4874-a383-1e0e7a829d12" type="Verb">
          <Vi>đánh giá; ước lượng; tính toán (giá trị, mức độ, mức đóng góp...)</Vi>
          <En>to evaluate or calculate the value, nature, or condition of something, especially for taxation or academic purposes</En>
          <Example>The teacher assessed the students' essays based on clarity and originality.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
